title: Draft Lessons, Free Agency Buzz with Brady Quinn (Football 5/2)
description:
Will Brinson and Brady Quinn debut a new intro music for the Pick Six Podcast, then dive into some draft lessons learned from the week that was in Nashville before breaking down possible free agent fits, the surprise moves some teams made in terms of picking up fifth year options and much more.
